create Role:
>kubectl create -f developer-role.yaml

Bind the user to that group
deveuser-binding.yaml

to list roles:
$kubectl get roles

to list role bindings
$kubectl get rolebindings

to describe role
$kubectl describe role role-name

to describe RoleBinding
$kubectl describe rolebinding rolebnding-name

Check access
$kubectl auth can-i create deployments
yes- you can
no- you can't
